axarapankti|अक्षरपङ्क्ति
Tatpur. f. (-ङ्क्तिः) Name of a verse or metre consisting of four lines, each of them containing one Dactylus and one Spondaeus ({??}), named also पङ्क्ति and हंस. E. अक्षर and पङ्क्ति.

axaramukha|अक्षरमुख
