axi|अक्षि
n. (-क्षि; for the declension of this word in the classical language see अक्षन्)<BR> ^1 The eye.<BR> ^2 This word is used sometimes to denote the numeral two. See also its synonymes नेत्र, लोचन &c. E. अश् (अशू) (or better अञ्ज्), uń. aff. क्सि.

axika|अक्षिक
