ankapaasha|अङ्कपाश
Tatpur. m. (-शः) Combination of numerals. E. अङ्क and पाश.

ankapaashavyavahaara|अङ्कपाशव्यवहार
Tatpur. m. (-रः) Concatenation of digits; a mutual mixing of the numbers, as it were a rope or halter of numerals: their variations being likened to a coil. E. अङ्कपाश and व्यवहार.

ankapaashaadhyaaya|अङ्कपाशाध्याय
