ankoTha|अङ्कोठ
m. (-ठः) A plant (Alangium hexapetalum). E. See अङ्कोट, ठ being used for ट.

ankola|अङ्कोल
m. (-लः) A plant. See अङ्कोट and अङ्कोठ; also अङ्कोलक.

ankolikaa|अङ्कोलिका
f. (-का) Embracing, an embrace. E. Contracted from अङ्कपालिका q. v., प being previously softened to व, and the inhering vowel dropped.

ankollasaara|अङ्कोल्लसार
Tatpur. m. (-रः) A kind of poison, probably prepared from the plant अङ्कोल, or अङ्कोट. E. अङ्कोल and सार, ल being doubled.

ankya|अङ्क्य
