angaarakadina|अङ्गारकदिन
Tatpur. m. n. (-नः-नम्) A festival on the fourteenth of the latter half of the month Chaitra, in honour of Angáraka or the planet Mars, in which certain ceremonies for the prevention of sin and disease are observed. E. अङ्गारक and दिन.

angaarakamaNi|अङ्गारकमणि
