aJNaataketa|अज्ञातकेत
Bahuvr. m. f. n. (-तः-ता-तम्) Having unknown or hidden designs. (In the Vedas.) E. अज्ञात and केत.

aJNaati|अज्ञाति
Tatpur. m. (-तिः) No kinsman or relation. E. अ neg. and ज्ञाति.

aJNaana|अज्ञान
I. Tatpur. n. (-नम्)<BR> ^1 Ignorance.<BR> ^2 Spiritual ignorance, worldly illusion or belief in external appearances. <BR>II. Bahuvr. m. f. n. (-नः-ना-नम्) Ignorant, unwise. E. अ neg. and ज्ञान.

aJNaanakRta|अज्ञानकृत
