anuukya|अनूक्य
(ved.) Tatpur. m. (-क्यः)<BR> ^1 The flesh of the skull.<BR> ^2 A joint of the bones (Sáyańa: = अस्थिसंधिः). E. अनु and उक्य (उच्, kŕitya aff. ण्यत्), according to Sáyańa; but perhaps a derivative of अनूक, taddh. aff. यत्.

anuuxam|अनूक्षम्
