antaHparidhaana|अन्तःपरिधान
Tatpur. n. (-नम्) A lower garment; of three or four garments either of the two which are nearest the body. Compare अन्तर. E. अन्तर् and परिधान.

antaHparidhi|अन्तःपरिधि
